;creod
INUMBER 691
NAME 25
MISC
SUBSTANCE BRITTLE
PARAMETER1 310
PARAMETER2 8
ARTICLE SOME
IFPREVERB LOOK -1
  CLEARVERB
  IFVAR INTNUM3 = 1
    ECHO PLAYER ****WARNING**** Do not touch this if it's val1 is above 1, Otherwise you will be hit by 50 random spells and call me nasty names... Gradrak.
  ENDIF
ENDIF
IFPREVERB TAP -1
  CLEARVERB
  IFVAR WIELDED = 766
    IFVAR FLAG3 ! 884
      IFVAR ITEMVAL5 = 3
        ECHO PLAYER You finish up the staff by shaping the butt of it. It is complete! You feel magically exhausted.
        ECHO OTHERS %N completes shaping the staff. %N looks ready to collapse.
        EQUAL ROUNDTIME 30
        EQUAL ITEMVAL5 4
        EQUAL FLAG3 884
        EQUAL MANAPOINTS 0
        REMOVEITEM -1
        IFNOITEM 7
          NEWITEM 7 1302 ADJ3=1049
        ELSE
          STRCVT 0 RNUM
          GMMSG A creod staff was failed to be created in room %0.  Please @add 1302 and give Adj3=1049.
          ECHO ALL This staff was not able to be created.  A message was sent to the GM staff. If nobody answers in 3 minutes, please assist.
        ENDIF
      ENDIF
      IFVAR ITEMVAL5 = 2
        ECHO PLAYER You tap the croed lightly, shaping this section into the lower section of a staff. This minor effort still drains all of the magical energy from you.
        ECHO OTHERS %N taps away at the creod. The lower shaft section of the staff takes shape. %N looks completely drained.
        EQUAL ROUNDTIME 30
        EQUAL ITEMVAL5 3
        EQUAL FLAG3 884
        EQUAL MANAPOINTS 0
      ENDIF
      IFVAR ITEMVAL5 = 1
        ECHO PLAYER Using delicate and precise strokes, you tap the creod into the upper shaft of a staff. This activity drains your magical energy.
        ECHO OTHERS %N delicately taps the creod and makes the upper half of a staff. %N look completely drained.
        EQUAL ROUNDTIME 30
        EQUAL ITEMVAL5 2
        EQUAL FLAG3 884
        EQUAL MANAPOINTS 0
      ENDIF
      IFVAR ITEMVAL5 = 0
        ECHO PLAYER You careful tap the creod with the hammer and shape the head od a staff into the brittle mineral. You magical power goes into this, leaving you drained.
        ECHO OTHERS %N uses the hammer to shape a staff's head into the creod. %N looks completely drained.
        EQUAL ROUNDTIME 30
        EQUAL ITEMVAL5 1
        EQUAL FLAG3 884
        EQUAL MANAPOINTS 0
      ENDIF
    ENDIF
  ENDIF
ENDIF
