IFPREVERB BREAK -1
  CLEARVERB
  ECHO PLAYER You hammer at the creod in an attempt to break it.
  ECHO OTHERS %N tries to destroy a piece of creod.
  IFVAR WIELDED = 766
    ECHO PLAYER You crush it into dust!
