INUMBER 1891
NAME 109
WEIGHT 1
VOLUME 1
IFVERB CONCENTRATE -1
	IFVAR ITEMVAL5 ! TIM
		EQUAL ITEMVAL5 TIM
		IFVAR REGION < 3
			ECHO PLAYER Blinding light envelopes you!  After a moment, your vision clears...
			MOVE ITEMVAL2
			ECHO OTHERS %N appears in a flash of light.
		ELSE
			ECHO PLAYER Nothing happens.
		ENDIF
	ELSE
		ECHO PLAYER Nothing happens.
	ENDIF
ENDIF
