      ECHO PLAYER You gaze into the depths of the crystal ball and see....nothing.
      ECHO OTHERS %N gazes into the crystal ball. By the look of disappointment on %h face you can tell %s saw nothing.
    ELSE
      ECHO PLAYER You gaze into the depths of the crystal balls' surface....in a matter of
