      IFVAR MUGCRYBALL = 2
        ECHO PLAYER You see a perfectly square shape of bone-white color. Six black pips are visible.
      ENDIF
      IFVAR MUGCRYBALL = 3
        ECHO PLAYER You see a perfectly square shape of bone-white color. Five black pips are visible.
      ENDIF
      IFVAR MUGCRYBALL = 4
        ECHO PLAYER You see a perfectly square shape of bone-white color. One black pips are visible.
      ENDIF
      IFVAR MUGCRYBALL = 5
        ECHO PLAYER You see a perfectly square shape of bone-white color. Two black pips are visible.
      ENDIF
      IFVAR MUGCRYBALL > 5
        ECHO PLAYER You see only a reddish mist.
        EQUAL MUGCRYBALL 0
      ENDIF
      ECHO PLAYER %cThe force of the knowledge delivered leaves you momentarily stunned.%c[Round: 10 sec]
      EQUAL ROUNDTIME 10
      EQUAL ITEMVAL5 0
      ECHO OTHERS %N locks %h gaze onto the crystal ball. The sudden loss of all expression upon %h face indicates something has occured.
    ENDIF
  ENDIF
ENDIF
