    ECHO PLAYER   %0       %1       %2
    ECHO PLAYER
    ECHO PLAYER
    ECHO PLAYER
    STRCVT 0 IDDEVSW
    STRCVT 1 IDDEVS
    STRCVT 2 IDDEVSE
    ECHO PLAYER   %0       %1       %2
    ECHO PLAYER
    AFFECT RNUM
    ECHO OTHERS %N looks into %a.
  ELSE
    ECHO PLAYER The device is small enough to fit comfortably within the palm of your hand and has a gray plastic cover over its front.
  ENDIF
