ENDIF
IFPREVERB LOOK -1
CLEARVERB
ECHO PLAYER You see the blackest, most vile-smelling concoction in existence. Your eyes%cbegin to water and you realize that if you keep looking at this "Medicine"%cthe fumes may blind you!
ENDIF
IFPREVERB DRINK -1
  IFVAR RAC = 6
    ECHO PLAYER As you drink the "medicine", your entire body stiffens in an uncontrollable,%chideous spasm. Just as you think you will pass out from the pain, your muscles%crelax considerably and you feel ...%c
    ECHO PLAYER HAPPY!
    ECHO OTHERS %N's eyes glaze over and %s grins stupidly at the world.
  ENDIF
  IFVAR RAC ! 6
    ECHO PLAYER As you drink the "medicine", your entire body goes into a hideous, jerking%cspasm. You begin to speak in tongues and your head feels like it is on fire,%cbut in a good way. Just as you think you can't take anymore, your knees give%cout and you 
    ECHO PLAYER fall to the ground.
    ECHO OTHERS %N looks like %s will be sick for a moment and then passes out.
    POSITION LAY
  ENDIF
ENDIF
