;chan'chalta
INUMBER 1300
NAME 708
FOOD
WEIGHT 1
VOLUME 1
SUBSTANCE CLOTH
ARTICLE some
PARAMETER1 5
IFPREVERB LOOK -1
  CLEARVERB
  ECHO PLAYER Inside this steel bowl is an assortment of chopped peppers, peppercorns, 
  ECHO PLAYER writhing Horthak, garlic, peppered cheese, scallions, red mushrooms, 
  ECHO PLAYER mandrake leaves, lettuce, cherry tomatoes, basil, cloves, onions, celery, 
  ECHO PLAYER and a few other things you can't even begin to name; all tossed into a sort 
  ECHO PLAYER of spicy salad with a dark green sauce. Steam rises from it and makes your 
  ECHO PLAYER eyes tear up. You are having serious doubts about eating this volatile 
  ECHO PLAYER concoction.
  ECHO OTHERS %N looks into a large steel bowl with a certain measure of fear.
ENDIF

IFVERB EAT -1
  IFVAR RAC = 6
    ECHO PLAYER As you stuff your mouth full of this spicy salad, you feel your body%ctemperature rise rapidly. Munching away contentedly, wisps of steam emanate%cfrom your nostrils as you make soft growling noises of sheer pleasure. As you 
    ECHO PLAYER finish off the last of it, you instantly consider ordering another bowl,%clicking your fingers to get the last of that delectable sauce.
    ECHO OTHERS %N attacks a bowl of Chan'chalta with gusto, happily munching away,%c%h eyes watering from the heat of this dish.
  ENDIF
  IFVAR RAC ! 6
    ECHO PLAYER You understand why this dish was served in a steel bowl; it's the only%csubstance that could hold it! Your mouth and throat feel as though you have%cjust swallowed a lava flow, with a slight hint of basil thrown in!
    ECHO OTHERS As %N takes a bite of the Chan'chalta, %N's eyes widen and %h body%cbecomes rigid with shock. Steam can be seen seeping from %N's nostrils!
    PLREVENT 4
    CONTPLREVENT
    ECHO PLAYER Gasping, you look around desperately for something to cool your ravaged%c throat.
    ECHO OTHERS %N runs around like a chicken with its head cut off yelling for%cwater at the top of %h lungs.
  ENDIF
ENDIF
